---
title: "Example 1"
format: typst
---

```{r}
library(typstable)
tt(mtcars[1:5, 1:3]) |>
  tt_column(mpg, align = "right") |>
  tt_row(1, bold = TRUE) |>
  tt_cell(2, 2, background = "yellow", content='12', colspan = 2, 
          rowspan = 2,
          align = 'center')
```

```{r}
df <- data.frame(
  col1 = c("First \\ Second", "Another"),
  col2 = c(1, 2)
)
tt(df, escape = FALSE)
```




